that control that you have.

00:38:55.980 --> 00:38:57.440
So you've got that use case.

00:38:57.440 --> 00:38:59.360
Don't forget goods movement.

00:38:59.360 --> 00:39:01.970
Over the road trucking--
the shortage of truck

00:39:01.970 --> 00:39:07.040
drivers or truck drivers, $0.64
