00:39:08.817 --> 00:39:10.400
It takes people away
from their homes,

00:39:10.400 --> 00:39:12.660
so there's real value
to be created there.

00:39:12.660 --> 00:39:15.470
And then finally, that
last mile of delivery.

00:39:15.470 --> 00:39:17.390
My goodness, I work
out of my home office.

00:39:17.390 --> 00:39:21.020
